3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a modulation scheme to improve the performance of a communication system, which is a topic related to systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the transmission of information using molecules, which can be considered a form of multimedia communication. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) - The concept of using molecular transmitters to transmit information can be applied to the field of robotics, which is a topic related to cs.RO.
